 eks of AIS data. By now you likely have enough — pause it to stop AWS cost.\n
 \nTO PAUSE (keeps all data, reversible):\n  cd /Users/loicns/Projects/data-pa
 rty-logistics\n  scripts/pause.sh\n\nTO RESUME LATER:\n  scripts/resume.sh\n\
 nFor near-$0 (also drop the CloudWatch dashboard) or full teardown, see SHUTD
 OWN.md in the project root.\n\nBEFORE pausing, consider rebuilding the Athena
  feature tables on the larger dataset and re-running build_dataset.py — you s
 hould now have 1000+ rows for real training.
